{%- liquid
  assign bg_color = section.settings.bg_color
  assign eye_color = section.settings.eye_color
  assign heading_color = section.settings.heading_color
  assign heading_italic_color = section.settings.heading_italic_color
  assign padding_top = section.settings.padding_top
  assign padding_bottom = section.settings.padding_bottom
  assign padding_x = section.settings.padding_x
  assign gap = section.settings.gap
  assign heading_size_desktop = section.settings.heading_size_desktop
  assign heading_size_mobile = section.settings.heading_size_mobile
  assign tab_size_desktop = section.settings.tab_size_desktop
  assign tab_size_mobile = section.settings.tab_size_mobile
  assign empty_size_desktop = section.settings.empty_size_desktop
  assign empty_size_mobile = section.settings.empty_size_mobile
  assign margin_top = section.settings.margin_top
  assign margin_bottom = section.settings.margin_bottom
  assign padding_top_mobile = section.settings.padding_top_mobile
  assign padding_bottom_mobile = section.settings.padding_bottom_mobile
  assign padding_x_mobile = section.settings.padding_x_mobile
  assign margin_top_mobile = section.settings.margin_top_mobile
  assign margin_bottom_mobile = section.settings.margin_bottom_mobile
  assign container_width = section.settings.container_width
  assign max_width = section.settings.max_width
  assign text_align = section.settings.text_align
  assign text_align_mobile = section.settings.text_align_mobile

  assign tab_count = 0
  for block in section.blocks
    if block.type == 'tab'
      assign tab_count = tab_count | plus: 1
    endif
  endfor
-%}

{%- comment -%}
  Bestsellers — KANSAWALA custom section (ported 9.0.0 → 9.1.0).
  Tabbed featured-products grid: each Tab block = one collection's panel.
  All panels render server-side (Liquid can't fetch); the JS toggles the
  active tab/panel. NO-JS-safe: the first panel defaults to .is-active and
  a base CSS rule keeps the first panel visible without JS.

  Structural + dynamic CSS is emitted inline below, scoped to
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} (self-contained — no shared section-common.css).
  Typography utilities (.t-*) + design tokens come from the shared
  foundation: assets/kw-typography.css + assets/kw-tokens.css, with fonts
  from snippets/kw-fonts.liquid. The tab engine is a self-booting IIFE in
  assets/theme.js (finds [data-section-type="bestsellers"] and binds).
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- style -%}
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} {
    background: {{ bg_color }};
    margin: {{ margin_top_mobile }}px 0 {{ margin_bottom_mobile }}px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    max-width: 100%;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-inner {
    padding: {{ padding_top }}px {{ padding_x }}px {{ padding_bottom }}px;
    {%- if container_width == 'boxed' -%}
    max-width: {{ max_width }}px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    {%- endif -%}
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-hdr > div { text-align: {{ text_align_mobile }}; }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-eye { justify-content: {% if text_align_mobile == 'center' %}center{% elsif text_align_mobile == 'right' %}flex-end{% else %}flex-start{% endif %}; }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-eye {
    color: {{ eye_color }};
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-ttl {
    line-height: 1.12;
    color: {{ heading_color }};
    font-size: {{ heading_size_desktop }}px;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-ttl em { color: {{ heading_italic_color }}; }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-hdr {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    /* `gap` (merchant setting, default 2px) controls the COLUMN gap only — kept tight on purpose.
       Row gap is a fixed, generous value so a small `gap` can't collapse the vertical spacing
       between wrapped rows (otherwise the next row's image touches the ATC button above it). */
    column-gap: {{ gap }}px;
    row-gap: 40px;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-grid .bsl-cell { min-width: 0; }

  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-empty {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    text-align: center;
    color: rgba(107,60,35,.55);
    padding: 32px 16px;
    font-size: {{ empty_size_desktop }}px;
  }

  /* ─── Tabs (real ARIA tablist) ─────────────────────────────────────── */
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(107,60,35,.18);
    overflow-x: auto;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-tabs::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  /* .bsl-tab pulls font-family / font-weight / text-transform / letter-spacing
     from .t-label + .t-label-tab in assets/kw-typography.css (which
     auto-tightens .14em -> .12em on mobile). Section-local rule sets size,
     color, and layout. */
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-tab {
    background: transparent;
    border: 0;
    padding: 12px 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: {{ tab_size_desktop }}px;
    color: rgba(107,60,35,.55);
    position: relative;
    transition: color .2s ease;
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-tab:hover { color: var(--K); }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-tab.is-active { color: var(--K); }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-tab.is-active::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -1px;
    left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--K);
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-tab:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid {{ heading_color }};
    outline-offset: 3px;
  }
  /* NO-JS-safe: hide every panel except the first; .is-active wins once JS
     toggles. The base rule keeps the first panel visible without JS. */
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-panel { display: none; }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-panel:first-of-type,
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-panel.is-active { display: block; }

  /* ─── Product card (faithful 9.0.0 kw-card, baked into .bsl-card) ──── */
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card {
    background: #FAF5EE;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--K);
    width: 100%;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__media {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 1/1;
    background: #FAF5EE;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: block;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: opacity .55s ease;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__img--secondary { position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: 0; }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__img { transition: none; }
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__placeholder {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; background: #FAF5EE;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: rgba(107,60,35,.25);
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__disc {
    position: absolute; top: 12px; left: 12px; z-index: 3;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center;
    background: var(--Br); color: #FAF5EE;
    border: 1px solid var(--Br); padding: 5px 10px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__media:focus-visible {
    outline: 3px solid {{ heading_color }};
    outline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__body {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    padding: 0 2px; flex: 1 1 auto;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__name {
    color: var(--K); margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-decoration: none;
    min-height: calc(16px * 1.5 * 2);
    transition: color .2s ease;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__name:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid {{ heading_color }};
    outline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__price {
    display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    color: var(--K);
    margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: auto;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__price-from {
    color: var(--K); font-family: var(--d);
    font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__price-amt {
    color: var(--K); font-family: var(--d);
    font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: .06em;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__price-amt::before { content: '\20B9 '; opacity: .7; margin-right: 1px; }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__price-orig {
    color: rgba(107,60,35,.70); font-family: var(--d);
    text-decoration: line-through; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: .06em;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__price-orig::before { content: '\20B9 '; opacity: .7; margin-right: 1px; }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__atc {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-start; text-align: left;
    width: 100%; padding: 11px 14px;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--K);
    border: 1px solid var(--K);
    cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
    transition: background .25s ease, color .25s ease, border-color .25s ease;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__atc:hover {
    background: var(--K);
    color: #FAF5EE;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__atc:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid {{ heading_color }};
    outline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__atc--disabled,
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__atc[disabled] {
    opacity: .55; cursor: not-allowed;
    background: transparent; color: var(--K);
    border-color: rgba(107,60,35,.30);
  }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__atc--disabled:hover { background: transparent; color: var(--K); }

  /* Review badge (product.metafields.reviews.rating) + tagline (product.metafields.custom.tagline) */
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__rate { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--K); }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__stars { position: relative; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; font-size: 0; }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__stars-row { display: inline-flex; gap: 2px; line-height: 0; }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__stars-row--fill { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; width: var(--rating-pct, 0%); }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__star { width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; display: block; }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__stars-row--bg .bsl-card__star { fill: #d8d4cf; }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__stars-row--fill .bsl-card__star { fill: var(--Br); }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__rate-count { color: var(--K); font-family: var(--d); font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: .02em; }
  .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__tag { font-family: var(--s); font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: .02em; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--Br); margin: 0 0 12px; }

  @media (max-width: 749px) {
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__star { width: 13px; height: 13px; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__rate { gap: 4px; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__rate-count { font-size: 13px; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__tag { font-size: 14px; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-ttl { font-size: {{ heading_size_mobile }}px; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-tabs { gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-tab { font-size: {{ tab_size_mobile }}px; padding: 10px 0; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-empty { font-size: {{ empty_size_mobile }}px; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__media { margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__disc { top: 10px; left: 10px; padding: 4px 8px; gap: 5px; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__atc { padding: 11px 13px; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__name { min-height: calc(14px * 1.5 * 2); }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__price-from { font-size: 13px; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__price-amt { font-size: 13px; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-card__price-orig { font-size: 13px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 749px) {
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} {
      margin: {{ margin_top_mobile }}px 0 {{ margin_bottom_mobile }}px !important;
    }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-inner {
      padding: {{ padding_top_mobile }}px {{ padding_x_mobile }}px {{ padding_bottom_mobile }}px;
    }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-hdr { text-align: {{ text_align_mobile }}; }
  }
  @media(min-width: 1024px) {
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} {
      margin: {{ margin_top }}px 0 {{ margin_bottom }}px;
    }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-hdr > div { text-align: {{ text_align }}; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-eye { justify-content: {% if text_align == 'center' %}center{% elsif text_align == 'right' %}flex-end{% else %}flex-start{% endif %}; }
    .bsl-{{ section.id }} .bsl-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }
  }
  {%- if section.settings.hide_desktop -%}
  @media (min-width: 768px) { .bsl-{{ section.id }} { display: none !important; } }
  {%- endif -%}
  {%- if section.settings.hide_mobile -%}
  @media (max-width: 749px) { .bsl-{{ section.id }} { display: none !important; } }
  {%- endif -%}
{%- endstyle -%}

<section class="bestsellers bsl-{{ section.id }}"
  data-section-id="{{ section.id }}"
  data-section-type="bestsellers"
  aria-labelledby="bsl-h-{{ section.id }}" {{ section.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="bsl-inner">
    <div class="bsl-hdr">
      <div>
        {%- if section.settings.eyebrow != blank -%}<div class="bsl-eye t-eyebrow t-eyebrow--dash">{{ section.settings.eyebrow | escape }}</div>{%- endif -%}
        <h2 class="bsl-ttl t-display" id="bsl-h-{{ section.id }}">{% if section.settings.heading != blank %}{{ section.settings.heading | escape }}{% endif %}{% if section.settings.heading_italic != blank %}<em>{{ section.settings.heading_italic | escape }}</em>{% endif %}</h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    {%- if tab_count > 0 -%}
      {%- comment -%} Tab mode — each Tab block = one collection panel {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="bsl-tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="{{ section.settings.heading | default: 'Bestsellers' | escape }}">
        {%- assign t_idx = 0 -%}
        {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
          {%- if block.type == 'tab' -%}
            {%- assign t_label = block.settings.label -%}
            {%- if t_label == blank and block.settings.collection != blank -%}
              {%- assign t_label = block.settings.collection.title -%}
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if t_label == blank -%}
              {%- assign t_label = 'Tab' -%}
            {%- endif -%}
            <button type="button"
              class="bsl-tab t-label t-label-tab{% if t_idx == 0 %} is-active{% endif %}"
              id="bsl-tab-{{ section.id }}-{{ t_idx }}"
              data-bsl-tab="{{ t_idx }}"
              data-block-id="{{ block.id }}"
              role="tab"
              aria-selected="{% if t_idx == 0 %}true{% else %}false{% endif %}"
              aria-controls="bsl-panel-{{ section.id }}-{{ t_idx }}"
              tabindex="{% if t_idx == 0 %}0{% else %}-1{% endif %}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
              {{ t_label | escape }}
            </button>
            {%- assign t_idx = t_idx | plus: 1 -%}
          {%- endif -%}
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>

      {%- assign t_idx = 0 -%}
      {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
        {%- if block.type == 'tab' -%}
          <div class="bsl-panel{% if t_idx == 0 %} is-active{% endif %}"
            id="bsl-panel-{{ section.id }}-{{ t_idx }}"
            data-bsl-panel="{{ t_idx }}"
            role="tabpanel"
            aria-labelledby="bsl-tab-{{ section.id }}-{{ t_idx }}"
            tabindex="0"{% if t_idx > 0 %} hidden{% endif %}>
            <div class="bsl-grid">
              {%- if block.settings.collection != blank and block.settings.collection.products.size > 0 -%}
                {%- for product in block.settings.collection.products limit: block.settings.product_count -%}
                  {%- liquid
                    assign img_loading = 'lazy'
                    assign img_fp = 'auto'
                    if t_idx == 0 and forloop.index <= 4
                      assign img_loading = 'eager'
                      assign img_fp = 'high'
                    endif
                    assign on_sale = false
                    if product.compare_at_price > product.price
                      assign on_sale = true
                    endif
                    assign discount_percent = 0
                    if on_sale
                      assign discount_percent = product.compare_at_price | minus: product.price | times: 100.0 | divided_by: product.compare_at_price | round
                    endif
                    assign primary_image = product.featured_media
                    assign secondary_image = blank
                    if product.media.size > 1
                      for media in product.media offset: 1 limit: 1
                        assign secondary_image = media
                      endfor
                    endif
                    assign first_variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant
                    assign alt_text = product.title | escape
                    assign rating_value = product.metafields.reviews.rating.value.rating | default: product.metafields.reviews.rating.value | default: 0
                    assign rating_count = product.metafields.reviews.rating_count | default: 0
                    assign has_rating = false
                    if rating_value != blank and rating_value != 0
                      assign has_rating = true
                    endif
                    assign tagline = product.metafields.custom.tagline
                  -%}
                  <div class="bsl-cell">
                    <article class="bsl-card">
                      <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="bsl-card__media" aria-label="{{ product.title | escape }}">
                        {%- if discount_percent > 0 and product.available -%}
                          <span class="bsl-card__disc t-label">{{ discount_percent }}% Off</span>
                        {%- endif -%}
                        {%- if primary_image != blank -%}
                          {{
                            primary_image
                            | image_url: width: 600
                            | image_tag:
                              class: 'bsl-card__img bsl-card__img--primary',
                              widths: '360, 540, 720, 900',
                              width: 600,
                              height: 600,
                              sizes: '(min-width: 750px) 25vw, 50vw',
                              alt: alt_text,
                              loading: img_loading,
                              fetchpriority: img_fp,
                              decoding: 'async'
                          }}
                        {%- else -%}
                          <div class="bsl-card__placeholder">{{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag: 'placeholder-svg' }}</div>
                        {%- endif -%}
                        {%- if secondary_image != blank -%}
                          {{
                            secondary_image
                            | image_url: width: 600
                            | image_tag:
                              class: 'bsl-card__img bsl-card__img--secondary',
                              widths: '360, 540, 720, 900',
                              width: 600,
                              height: 600,
                              sizes: '(min-width: 750px) 25vw, 50vw',
                              alt: '',
                              loading: 'lazy',
                              decoding: 'async',
                              aria-hidden: 'true'
                          }}
                        {%- endif -%}
                      </a>
                      <div class="bsl-card__body">
                        {%- if has_rating -%}
                          {%- assign rating_pct = rating_value | times: 20.0 -%}
                          <div class="bsl-card__rate" aria-label="Rated {{ rating_value }} out of 5{% if rating_count > 0 %} from {{ rating_count }} reviews{% endif %}">
                            <span class="bsl-card__stars" aria-hidden="true" style="--rating-pct:{{ rating_pct }}%;">
                              <span class="bsl-card__stars-row bsl-card__stars-row--bg">{%- for i in (1..5) -%}<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="bsl-card__star"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>{%- endfor -%}</span>
                              <span class="bsl-card__stars-row bsl-card__stars-row--fill">{%- for i in (1..5) -%}<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="bsl-card__star"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>{%- endfor -%}</span>
                            </span>
                            {%- if rating_count > 0 -%}<span class="bsl-card__rate-count">{{ rating_count }} Reviews</span>{%- endif -%}
                          </div>
                        {%- endif -%}
                        <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="bsl-card__name t-card-name">{{ product.title | escape }}</a>
                        {%- if tagline != blank -%}<p class="bsl-card__tag">{{ tagline | escape }}</p>{%- endif -%}
                        <div class="bsl-card__price">
                          {%- if product.price_varies -%}
                            <span class="bsl-card__price-from">From</span>
                            <span class="bsl-card__price-amt">{{ product.price_min | money_without_currency | replace: '.00', '' }}</span>
                          {%- else -%}
                            <span class="bsl-card__price-from">{% if on_sale %}Sale{% else %}MRP{% endif %}</span>
                            <span class="bsl-card__price-amt">{{ product.price | money_without_currency | replace: '.00', '' }}</span>
                            {%- if on_sale -%}
                              <span class="bsl-card__price-orig" aria-label="Original price">{{ product.compare_at_price | money_without_currency | replace: '.00', '' }}</span>
                            {%- endif -%}
                          {%- endif -%}
                        </div>
                        {%- if product.available -%}
                          {%- if product.has_only_default_variant -%}
                            {%- form 'product', product, class: 'bsl-card__atc-form' -%}
                              <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{ first_variant.id }}">
                              <button type="submit" class="bsl-card__atc t-card-cta" aria-label="Add {{ product.title | escape }} to cart">
                                <span class="bsl-card__atc-label">Add to Cart</span>
                              </button>
                            {%- endform -%}
                          {%- else -%}
                            <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="bsl-card__atc t-card-cta" aria-label="Add {{ product.title | escape }} to cart — pick a size on the product page">
                              <span class="bsl-card__atc-label">Add to Cart</span>
                            </a>
                          {%- endif -%}
                        {%- else -%}
                          <button type="button" class="bsl-card__atc bsl-card__atc--disabled t-card-cta" disabled aria-label="{{ product.title | escape }} is sold out">
                            <span class="bsl-card__atc-label">Sold Out</span>
                          </button>
                        {%- endif -%}
                      </div>
                    </article>
                  </div>
                {%- endfor -%}
              {%- else -%}
                <p class="bsl-empty t-body">
                  {%- if request.design_mode -%}Pick a collection for this tab.{%- else -%}{{ section.settings.empty | default: 'Products coming soon.' | escape }}{%- endif -%}
                </p>
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>
          </div>
          {%- assign t_idx = t_idx | plus: 1 -%}
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    {%- elsif request.design_mode -%}
      <p class="bsl-empty t-body" style="display:block;">Add a “Tab” block to populate this grid.</p>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>
</section>

{%- comment -%}
  Tab switcher lives in a self-booting IIFE in assets/theme.js. The section
  root carries data-section-type="bestsellers"; the IIFE finds and binds
  every instance, toggles .is-active + ARIA state, supports roving tabindex
  + ←/→/Home/End keyboard nav, re-inits on shopify:section:load, and (in the
  editor) activates the selected tab on shopify:block:select. init-once via
  data-bsl-booted.
{%- endcomment -%}

